rows.label: tlk000010_msg0001
rows.name: Hello. To whom do I owe the pleasure?

rows.label: tlk000010_msg0002
rows.name:
Yes, we'd already received word from
Special Inquisitor Meleph.

rows.label: tlk000010_msg0003
rows.name:
You've a lead on the artificial Blade,
I hear?

rows.label: tlk000010_msg0004
rows.name:
Hold on, I'll pass you over to the
Special Inquisitor herself.
